title: Gated Community, Onsite Management, Pet Friendly!
posting_body: ['Designed for modern luxury living, the newly renovated apartment homes at The Meadows offer the lifestyle you desire.', 'Our pet-friendly one and two bedroom apartments in Tacoma, Washington, feature open-concept floor plans with spacious living areas.', 'Sleek stainless-steel appliances, handsome custom cabinetry, and warm wood-style plank flooring are a few of the finishes that add elegance to your space.', 'Each home includes a covered balcony or patio where you can kick back and relax in the fresh air with your pup.', 'Resort-style amenities await at The Meadows.', 'Treat yourself to a refreshing swimming pool, 24-hour fitness center, and a stylish clubhouse with fireplace lounge and complimentary WiFi.', 'Exceptional living begins here.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Swimming Pool', 'Oversized Walk-In Closet', 'Playground', 'Private Balcony', 'Gated Electronic Entrance', 'Coffee Station & Cafe Lounge', '24-Hour Fitness center', 'Microwave', 'Resident Events', 'Full-Sized Washer and Dryer', 'Refreshing Swimming Pool & Year-Round Spa', 'Online Payments Available', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
